    "We use 70% of the data for training and the remaining 30% for testing.",
    "The values show the proportion of predictions in the test set falling within a given category (columns) given the observed major field (rows).",
    "\"Electrical Engineering\" is short for \"Electrical Engineering and Systems Science\" among its k nearest neighbors (see Methods).",
    "We show in Fig. 1b the confusion matrix obtained on the remaining 30% of the data.",
    "Overall, we find an average prediction accuracy of 77.8%."
